Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.81,0:01:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  阿土
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.36,0:01:35.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個週日跟我出去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.97,0:01:38.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行不行  週日我很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.59,0:01:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥？！  很忙是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.44,0:01:44.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…大人有很多事情要做的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.82,0:01:48.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大人的事情？  難道說背著小杏還有別的女朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.12,0:01:51.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那樣的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.28,0:01:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼能這樣  好過分！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.00,0:01:57.28,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}快點快點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.73,0:01:59.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然他說了沒有別的女朋友  但那態度太可疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.13,0:02:03.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定他不來找我約會也都是因為外面有人了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.84,0:02:07.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照土田老師的情況很有那個可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.00,0:02:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟阿土那麼帥嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.32,0:02:13.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算他自己沒那個意思可能也會有女孩子黏過來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.14,0:02:18.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有必要調查週日他到底在做什麼  你也接這種工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.26,0:02:21.39,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（真相只有一個）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.73,0:02:21.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受各種各樣工作委託的就是所謂的偵探
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.56,0:02:23.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這個啦  小杏要當偵探
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.11,0:02:28.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此  情況我瞭解了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.31,0:02:29.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過只有你們幾個沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.98,0:02:32.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題  就在附近轉轉而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.33,0:02:33.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個借我用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.92,0:02:35.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是有什麼事情馬上打電話回來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.28,0:02:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.06,0:02:41.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}花丸偵探團
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.40,0:02:48.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  又得重新來過了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.40,0:02:48.39,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（這究竟是Boss戰忘存檔了還是迷宮中迷路了）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:53.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再睡個回籠覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:55.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.93,0:03:00.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  我是土田
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.87,0:03:02.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿土  上午好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.59,0:03:05.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是小杏啊  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.29,0:03:06.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼大清早打電話來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.67,0:03:09.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是大清早呢  都中午了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.28,0:03:10.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中午？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.32,0:03:12.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你現在在家嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.32,0:03:14.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.70,0:03:20.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事啦  好不容易有個星期天宅在家裡太浪費了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.34,0:03:23.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她搞什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.22,0:03:28.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿土還在家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:32.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身為偵探卻給偵查對像打電話這算是什麼事啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.84,0:03:35.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,土田老師出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.33,0:03:40.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「一整天都宅在家裡太浪費了」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.00,0:03:46.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼接下來我們就開始對阿土進行跟…跟…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.69,0:03:47.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個叫什麼來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.95,0:03:48.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.77,0:03:51.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  開始進行跟蹤吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.31,0:03:55.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花丸偵探團  出動啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.76,0:04:15.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎麼覺得好像被人盯著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.38,0:04:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是錯覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.54,0:04:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小杏  那裡有隻小貓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.88,0:04:26.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是小貓咪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.10,0:04:29.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  好可愛呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.27,0:04:30.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.24,0:04:33.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小杏  我們還要跟蹤呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.66,0:04:39.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真令人懷念呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.56,0:04:44.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是日向誠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.56,0:04:44.60,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（Nerv中央作戰司令部成員，豪無存在感的某隻）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:46.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能抽到綾波嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.61,0:04:50.85,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（星印冰淇淋）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.64,0:04:54.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抽了一大堆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.32,0:04:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要的抽不出來就認真較上勁了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.57,0:04:58.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所謂的大人買法啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.57,0:04:58.65,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（註釋：食玩等原本面向兒童的商品，成年人卻去批量購入的現象，\N也泛指個人一次性購入大量商品的情況）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.62,0:05:07.04,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}EVA新劇場版：破
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.62,0:05:07.04,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}2009年初夏上映
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.62,0:05:07.04,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}扭蛋作戰啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.12,0:05:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他喜歡這樣的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.46,0:05:09.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  這裡有熊喵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.54,0:05:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:12.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,100日元有點貴了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.13,0:05:15.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小梅身上帶著100日元的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.37,0:05:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要抽一個看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:17.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.43,0:05:19.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小杏  小梅  我們還要跟蹤啊跟蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.93,0:05:21.95,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（花丸商業街）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:29.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要小心  不要把土田老師跟丟了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:31.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  小杏會注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.11,0:05:33.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  好奇怪的招牌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.97,0:05:36.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的  真好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.98,0:05:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然幼稚園孩子當偵探是不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.08,0:05:48.39,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（家庭餐館  天空漢堡）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.42,0:05:51.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他進了家庭餐館了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.32,0:05:53.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是跟情人約好在這見面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.40,0:05:54.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:06:01.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,土田老師笑瞇瞇的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.34,0:06:04.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是在等心愛的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.07,0:06:08.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣  阿土你個大騙子！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.85,0:06:12.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿土大笨蛋  阿土大笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.73,0:06:14.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一直笑瞇瞇的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.16,0:06:16.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.86,0:06:18.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.25,0:06:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等的人一直沒來他卻心情很好的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.67,0:06:27.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定他只是看到女招待感覺很滿足而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.87,0:06:33.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可愛啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.92,0:06:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  那邊那個胸部真有料啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:43.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來被我猜中了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:45.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這家店的制服很可愛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.72,0:06:51.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小杏我才不會在意呢  至少比另有情人來得好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.54,0:06:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿土你也太遜了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.07,0:07:01.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個偶像終於拍脫衣寫真了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.75,0:07:04.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在看小黃本…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:05.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小黃本…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.07,0:07:07.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小黃本是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.46,0:07:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那也是沒辦法的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.37,0:07:14.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,電視上說了  健全的男人就應該對那些有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.24,0:07:21.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小杏才不會因為這點事情就放棄呢  我不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.07,0:07:22.34,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}啊  真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.86,0:07:33.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好  不能和他們目光對上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.09,0:07:41.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才的扭蛋…這個就不要了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.70,0:07:42.92,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（留下的是明日香和綾波？）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.98,0:07:45.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  這位小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.99,0:07:49.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對  說的就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.76,0:07:51.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請…請問有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.71,0:07:53.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有話要對你說  過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.42,0:07:57.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有…有話要說？  我可沒什麼好說的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:08:00.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還不照組長說的老實過來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.98,0:08:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,組長？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.26,0:08:05.87,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}別別別別…我才不過去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:06.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,土田老師怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.68,0:08:08.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師好像被人找碴了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.90,0:08:08.23,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}叫你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.70,0:08:09.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找碴？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.03,0:08:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是被壞人纏上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.49,0:08:12.53,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}呃  我又沒惹著你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.83,0:08:13.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快過來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.84,0:08:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大事不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.88,0:08:19.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,廢話少說  跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.08,0:08:21.23,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}我說你們幾個！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.29,0:08:21.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請不要使用暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.35,0:08:25.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻…學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.01,0:08:26.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.04,0:08:31.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算做什麼？  對這麼人畜無害的男生使用暴力？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.91,0:08:33.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人畜無害？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.53,0:08:36.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你再不放手我就要報警了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.38,0:08:37.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說啊…這位大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.95,0:08:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不記得有你這個弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.30,0:08:46.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈…膽識不錯  真是位有意思的大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:49.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過你好像有點誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.52,0:08:59.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們只不過想提醒一下這位小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.27,0:09:01.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他沒有把垃圾扔到該扔的地方而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:08.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們組正在做一些和社區密切相關的活動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.22,0:09:09.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.17,0:09:11.64,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}愛清潔，講衛生，靠你靠我靠大家！\N花丸商業街
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:17.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  今後我會注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.04,0:09:19.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.47,0:09:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來  我很中意大姐你的氣魄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.69,0:09:25.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有緣再見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:26.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  好好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:30.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又讓學姐救了我一次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.68,0:09:34.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從學生時代起就沒一點進步呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.32,0:09:36.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你比學生時代長進多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.70,0:09:39.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是以前的阿土的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.51,0:09:42.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光是被那些人搭個話就會嚇得哭出來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.06,0:09:44.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說得好過分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.71,0:09:48.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來  學姐在這裡做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:55.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了對了  我還有事呢  回頭見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.34,0:10:00.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她還是跟從前一樣有活力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.19,0:10:05.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我不清楚前因後果  但總之是媽媽救了阿土？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.31,0:10:06.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.42,0:10:12.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟著她們幾個的事情沒曝露吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.47,0:10:29.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們約去喝酒是下週的事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.71,0:10:34.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？  有戀人了？…對你？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.35,0:10:36.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊…那不是挺好的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.89,0:10:38.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.12,0:10:43.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說我啊？雖然我有中意的人但是關係毫無進展
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.04,0:10:46.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且工作上還不太習慣…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.33,0:10:49.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.64,0:10:51.64,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,是要去約會吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:54.01,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,要喝酒的話我隨時奉陪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.62,0:10:57.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此  他約好了和某個女人一起去喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.15,0:10:57.04,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}下次再聯絡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.41,0:11:02.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是她已經有了戀人了所以要和那個人去約會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.09,0:11:00.10,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}啊  知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.74,0:11:02.36,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}我要是有什麼事的話再打電話給你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.27,0:11:04.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他看起來反而很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.12,0:11:05.86,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}那我先掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.82,0:11:07.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他中意的人一定是指小杏我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:12.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來下週的週日也沒有安排了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.41,0:11:19.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社會人的休息日也就是這麼回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.40,0:11:23.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,土田老師看上去好寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:28.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.05,0:11:35.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.20,0:11:37.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿土
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.33,0:11:41.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打起精神來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.21,0:11:46.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小杏  小柊  小梅  你們幾個在這裡做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿土本來預定去約會卻被對方甩了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.30,0:11:53.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約會？被甩？你在說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.46,0:11:55.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿土好可憐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.27,0:11:59.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼哭了？為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.56,0:12:04.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…是嗎  因為這個才跟著我的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.04,0:12:08.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我總是在擔心你有沒有花心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.37,0:12:10.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.79,0:12:16.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們幾個想不想吃鯛魚燒？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.14,0:12:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我前一陣發現了一家很棒的店
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.91,0:12:21.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鯛魚燒？！要去要去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.80,0:12:24.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鯛魚燒要吃從頭到尾都塞滿豆餡的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.46,0:12:28.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偵探團的活動到此結束了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.75,0:12:30.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過阿土還真是讓人不放心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.22,0:12:32.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其是私生活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.31,0:12:40.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小杏不會在意阿土你白看小黃本的事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.01,0:12:44.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你色瞇瞇地盯著女招待看我也原諒你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.02,0:12:48.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們連那些都看到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.33,0:12:49.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我們是偵探啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:52.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…我丟人的一面全都給看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.66,0:13:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不倒翁呀  摔倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.24,0:13:06.77,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（123木頭人的遊戲而已）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.45,0:13:15.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿土  來說說我們的將來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.17,0:13:16.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  等會兒再說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.86,0:13:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不等呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.03,0:13:19.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小杏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:26.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小杏  好個餓虎撲食
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.21,0:13:29.23,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,小杏想要一棟有庭院的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:31.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小杏等等我  小梅也要一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.26,0:13:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要養狗狗  還要生好多孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.58,0:13:38.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小杏  小柊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.36,0:13:40.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.68,0:13:44.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒受傷吧  能站起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.41,0:13:52.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:13:59.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優  我們快點出去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.80,0:14:00.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.60,0:14:02.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.29,0:14:04.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.58,0:14:07.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能在走廊亂跑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.35,0:14:11.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.21,0:14:13.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}花丸初戀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.09,0:14:17.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小梅  扔下你一個人真對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.46,0:14:19.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小梅？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.88,0:14:25.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那個…這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.26,0:14:27.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.69,0:14:29.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小梅摔倒了以後…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.53,0:14:30.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.66,0:14:37.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那個孩子對小梅伸出援手的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.48,0:14:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別人好像叫他優
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.57,0:14:42.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們在做什麼？  師父
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.10,0:14:43.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要扔了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.88,0:14:47.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是優  大悟和悠斗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:48.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.18,0:14:52.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,健治同學  你認識他們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.38,0:14:54.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們可是同在向日葵班的同學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.46,0:14:59.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說師父啊  「健治同學」這個叫法太生分了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.74,0:15:01.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接叫「健治」就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.37,0:15:03.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.12,0:15:05.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你啦  師父
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.79,0:15:10.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,調查完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.28,0:15:15.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從老師和其他同學那裡收集到了相關資料
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.30,0:15:20.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他名叫小早川優  向日葵中班
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.29,0:15:21.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家中共有四人  其中他是長子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.66,0:15:26.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父親是外交官  血型是O型  喜歡的食物是漢堡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.84,0:15:31.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中班的啊  跟阿土比起來還是個小鬼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.92,0:15:33.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.42,0:15:35.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿土比他帥多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.57,0:15:37.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優也很帥的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.55,0:15:41.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那小梅快去表白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.79,0:15:47.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只要一想到優就會覺得胸口發緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.36,0:15:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到他的笑容就會心跳不止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.47,0:15:54.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是愛啊  快去表白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.96,0:15:57.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小杏我每天都在對阿土表白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.13,0:16:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是小杏  真會強詞奪理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.43,0:16:04.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但或許小杏說的是對的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.37,0:16:05.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.47,0:16:10.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定明天優就要搬家了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.01,0:16:09.83,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.47,0:16:15.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定明天他就會被外星人捉走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.95,0:16:18.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定明天會爆發第二次衝擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.95,0:16:18.76,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（EVA的NETA就算了）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.10,0:16:21.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又可能會爆發伊修巴爾戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.10,0:16:21.03,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（不過水島你NETA鋼鍊是想提醒大家自己是03版的監督吧）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.35,0:16:23.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗚嗚…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.40,0:16:24.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.77,0:16:26.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  我胡扯過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.25,0:16:30.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.25,0:16:33.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說得沒錯  小梅要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.06,0:16:36.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要好好地對優道謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.66,0:16:39.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我能做到嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.84,0:16:45.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題  只要像小杏一樣好好磨練出女人味  一定能手到擒來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.49,0:16:46.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女人味？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.99,0:16:47.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,磨練？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.11,0:16:50.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天的護膚保養都不能偷懶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.51,0:16:52.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後面對鏡子練習微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.13,0:16:56.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在浴室裡做按摩和半身泡澡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.75,0:16:58.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再不出來就泡暈了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.34,0:17:02.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還不能出來  要為了阿土變得更漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.98,0:17:06.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杏我明明這麼健康可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.18,0:17:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿土卻因為在意世人的眼光不肯把我當作戀愛對象
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.19,0:17:13.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿土大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.66,0:17:15.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小杏  你開始跑題了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.97,0:17:19.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果當面說你覺得不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:20.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼用寫信的方式怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.93,0:17:22.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.42,0:17:26.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小杏也來寫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.92,0:17:28.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寫什麼好呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.80,0:17:31.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寫下你現在最真實的想法就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.68,0:17:32.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.50,0:17:38.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寫好了  我去把情書拿給阿土看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.59,0:17:40.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「謝謝你」要怎麼寫呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.94,0:17:46.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然小梅不會寫的話  說不定優也不會讀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.82,0:17:50.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我果然不行嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.10,0:17:52.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,問題在於你們倆的年齡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.11,0:17:56.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看  阿土給了我小紅花
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.11,0:17:56.24,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（つっちーあいしてる：阿土我愛你）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.11,0:17:56.24,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（註釋：這個符號就是所謂的「花丸」，常常用來獎勵小朋友功課做得好等等）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.99,0:17:58.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小梅你的情書寫得怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.17,0:18:01.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寫信可能太難了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.33,0:18:05.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是覺得寫長信太難的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.35,0:18:08.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就寫上一句道謝  加上一點小禮物怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.72,0:18:11.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽上去好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.48,0:18:15.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禮物就選小梅自己想要送給他的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.89,0:18:21.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優  有女孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.04,0:18:25.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.24,0:18:27.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才的小班生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.26,0:18:29.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經不要緊了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.06,0:18:31.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.03,0:18:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.77,0:18:44.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗚…彈子掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:45.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一起撿起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.11,0:18:46.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.91,0:18:50.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優還蠻有紳士風度的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.95,0:18:56.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我太緊張了  都沒和優說上話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.29,0:19:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是所謂的戀愛啊  酸酸甜甜的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.28,0:19:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去把優叫過來  說不定就不會緊張了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.03,0:19:05.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小梅你等著就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.33,0:19:08.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣或許比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:11.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那個吧  「在校舍後面對你表白」什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.98,0:19:14.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,氣氛很重要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.76,0:19:16.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去叫優過來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.66,0:19:22.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道為什麼覺得好興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.38,0:19:26.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小杏和小柊為了小梅我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.73,0:19:30.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來一定要好好對優說聲謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.49,0:19:33.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  接下來考慮一下表白的時候要說的台詞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.76,0:19:35.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表白的台詞？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.63,0:19:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小杏知道一句必殺的台詞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.64,0:19:42.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣優一定會迷上你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.00,0:19:43.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.91,0:19:46.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在說什麼呢  商量怎麼惡作劇嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.83,0:19:47.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,土田老師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.16,0:19:49.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是惡作劇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.67,0:19:51.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在幫小梅商量表白的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.07,0:19:54.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表白？小梅嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.65,0:19:55.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小杏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.68,0:19:57.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  糟了  說漏嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.68,0:20:00.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然對小杏來說這種事已經是家常便飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.87,0:20:03.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,輪到小梅可就讓人有些擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.88,0:20:07.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承蒙您在百忙之中抽空來一趟  真是不勝感激
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.13,0:20:11.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是小梅嗎  她找我有事？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.27,0:20:15.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.15,0:20:19.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小梅  你加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.45,0:20:20.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.94,0:20:25.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.08,0:20:28.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那個  優
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.81,0:20:29.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.98,0:20:32.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有話對你說…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.45,0:20:35.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小梅  感覺不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.37,0:20:36.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.48,0:20:37.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.60,0:20:41.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱…抱我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.41,0:20:43.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.52,0:20:48.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱你？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.96,0:20:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽她啊  就是這樣對爸爸表白的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.78,0:20:54.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要說的事情是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.54,0:20:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說了剛才那句話就應該成功的才對…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.62,0:21:05.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  優  還沒好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.15,0:21:07.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都說好了要在外面玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.14,0:21:10.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我馬上就去  再等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.82,0:21:11.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.99,0:21:18.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優為了我推遲了和朋友的約定…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.68,0:21:22.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那個…優！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.19,0:21:23.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.26,0:21:26.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.71,0:21:33.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛…剛才謝謝你幫了小梅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.51,0:21:36.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直想對你說聲謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.64,0:21:41.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  不用客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.39,0:21:42.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.66,0:21:44.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起啊  終於說出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.32,0:21:46.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.89,0:21:47.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小梅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.76,0:21:50.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起出去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.46,0:21:54.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青春啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.86,0:21:56.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是託小杏的福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.76,0:21:57.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.01,0:23:33.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.43,0:23:34.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小梅  加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.64,0:23:36.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…抱…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.74,0:23:37.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…抱我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.58,0:23:38.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.51,0:23:42.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一集輪到土田老師的妹妹  五月姐登場
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.65,0:23:44.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有有關游泳池的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.62,0:23:45.97,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}花丸泳池  花丸作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.62,0:23:45.97,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}花丸哥哥  花丸留宿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.38,0:23:45.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬請期待
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.75,0:22:10.99,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}あのね　だいすきだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.60,0:22:17.00,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}あのね　なみだがでるの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.11,0:22:29.72,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}かくれ　たいな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.96,0:22:36.96,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}そっと　うつむいて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.18,0:22:42.67,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}育てた花
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.06,0:22:48.71,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}やっと　咲きました
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.95,0:22:54.67,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}もっと　そばにゆきたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.89,0:23:00.77,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}もっと　はやく走りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.98,0:23:06.89,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}ランラ　空をみあげて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.09,0:23:12.83,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}わたし　つよくなるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.04,0:23:19.88,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}わたし　つよくなるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.75,0:22:10.99,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs25}{\fad(300,300)}吶　我最喜歡你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.60,0:22:17.00,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs25}{\fad(300,300)}吶　我都快要哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.11,0:22:29.72,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs25}{\fad(300,300)}好想找個地方藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.96,0:22:36.96,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs25}{\fad(300,300)}偷偷低著頭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.18,0:22:42.67,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs25}{\fad(300,300)}生長著的小花
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.06,0:22:48.71,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs25}{\fad(300,300)}終於開出了美麗的花瓣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.95,0:22:54.67,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs25}{\fad(300,300)}好想到你的身邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.89,0:23:00.77,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs25}{\fad(300,300)}好想再跑得快些啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.98,0:23:06.89,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs25}{\fad(300,300)}仰起頭看著天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.09,0:23:12.83,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs25}{\fad(300,300)}我會變得更加堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.04,0:23:19.88,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs25}{\fad(300,300)}我會變得更加堅強
